#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:77
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_STORE_SNIPER_SIEGED\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Looks like an EXTREME-ly deadly stealth ship is attacking the nearby market owned by a certain \"Sniper Girl\". If you can stop them, you should be able to access the store.\n"
"\t\tThe specialized store looks ready to provide fire support."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:82
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_STORE_SNIPER_SIEGED\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Rescue the store."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:84
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_STORE_SNIPER_SIEGED\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "You prepare for combat."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:88
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_STORE_SNIPER_SIEGED\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:94
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_STORE_SNIPER_SIEGED\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Ignore the merchant."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:96
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_STORE_SNIPER_SIEGED\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You are pretty sure they noticed your presence, but they seem too busy to "
"care."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:98
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_STORE_SNIPER_SIEGED\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:102
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_STORE_SNIPER_SIEGED\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:112
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_STORE_SNIPER_EXTREME\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "The stealth ship breaks apart and you quickly salvage what you can."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:115
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_STORE_SNIPER_EXTREME\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:120
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_STORE_SNIPER_EXTREME\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"With the crew dead you quickly salvage what you can from the stealth ship."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:123
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_STORE_SNIPER_EXTREME\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:130
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_STORE_SNIPER_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Sniper Girl wastes no time hailing you. \"They just keep coming, with better equipment every time, to rob us. I just can't catch a breath. I know that's why you're here too...\" You're about to say something to cheer her up when she cuts you off. \"Because there's NO better shop in this universe for Stealth gear! So efficient, pirates dream about it, coalitions plot to acquire it, and renegades jump in to steal it! Buy while you still can!\".\n"
"\t\tTurns out she's still in character. RK sector professionals must have seen some shit, you think to yourself.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\"...And for your timely assistance, here's a little incentive to buy.\" You realize the gift is your \"Thank you\", and shrug.\n"
"\t\tThen you take one look at the wares and immediately understand why the attacker came here.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\"Oh and, some of this stuff is so hard to source it shouldn't even exist, so only 1 purchase per customer. But for you I'll make it 3.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:142
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_STORE_SNIPER_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Alright then."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:154
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_FIGHT_ELITE_COALITION\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The elite Coalition ship here is flying away from the fresh wreck of an unlucky smuggler. They sound very excited on the open comms.\n"
"\t\t\"Ok we have steal good weapons. Now, must test! I see prey here, gogogo!\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:160
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_FIGHT_ELITE_COALITION\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_nights\"]/text"
msgstr "(Nights) Tell them to bugger off."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:162
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_FIGHT_ELITE_COALITION\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_nights\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Go find a different ship to test that on, fools!\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\"Oh shit, Nights on that ship? Tkkkktk. Power engines, must find preyyyy!\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:167
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_FIGHT_ELITE_COALITION\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_nights\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:174
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_FIGHT_ELITE_COALITION\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_tyrdeo\"]/text"
msgstr "(Tyrdeo) Tell them to bugger off."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:176
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_FIGHT_ELITE_COALITION\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_tyrdeo\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Go find a different ship to test that on, please!\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\"Oh shit, Tyrdeo on that ship? Tkkkktk. Power engines, must find preyyyy!\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:181
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_FIGHT_ELITE_COALITION\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_tyrdeo\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:188
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_FIGHT_ELITE_COALITION\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Defend yourself!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:190
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_FIGHT_ELITE_COALITION\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr "You prepare for combat."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:193
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_FIGHT_ELITE_COALITION\"]/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:226
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_SUSPICIOUS_SMUGGLER\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The ship hiding at this hazardous beacon has no conspicuous pirate markings,"
" but behaves very strangely. You suspect it's a smuggler. Fighting it will "
"certainly destroy whatever cargo they're hiding."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:231
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_SUSPICIOUS_SMUGGLER\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_POLICE_WARRANT\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "Without a Police Warrant, you can't submit them to a search."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:236
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_SUSPICIOUS_SMUGGLER\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_POLICE_WARRANT\""
" and not(@lvl)]/text"
msgstr "(Police Warrant) Demand to search them"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:239
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_SUSPICIOUS_SMUGGLER\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_POLICE_WARRANT\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Oh god dammit, you're with those Zoltan party poopers? Just my luck... I'm not risking our lives over this, come on in.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\tAfter a thorough search, you find their RK augment! You're supposed to drop it off at the Police Station marked on your map, but keeping it could help with your more important mission."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:246
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_SUSPICIOUS_SMUGGLER\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_POLICE_WARRANT\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event[1]/choice/text"
msgstr "Nice!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:251
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_SUSPICIOUS_SMUGGLER\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_POLICE_WARRANT\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Oh god dammit, you're with those Zoltan party poopers? Just my luck... I'm not risking our lives over this, come on in.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\tAfter a thorough search, you find their RK weaponry! You're supposed to drop it off at the Police Station marked on your map, but keeping it could help with your more important mission."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:258
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_SUSPICIOUS_SMUGGLER\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_POLICE_WARRANT\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event[2]/choice/text"
msgstr "Nice!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:264
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_SUSPICIOUS_SMUGGLER\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_POLICE_WARRANT\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event[3]/text"
msgstr "They immediately start powering their weapons!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:267
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_SUSPICIOUS_SMUGGLER\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_POLICE_WARRANT\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event[3]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:274
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_SUSPICIOUS_SMUGGLER\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Attack them!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:276
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_SUSPICIOUS_SMUGGLER\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr "You prepare for combat."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:279
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_SUSPICIOUS_SMUGGLER\"]/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:286
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_SUSPICIOUS_SMUGGLER\"]/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "Don't do anything."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:288
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_SUSPICIOUS_SMUGGLER\"]/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You don't approach, but the ship seems aware that you noticed them. \"Hey, "
"uh, what are you looking at?\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:290
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_SUSPICIOUS_SMUGGLER\"]/choice[4]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Oh, you know..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:292
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_SUSPICIOUS_SMUGGLER\"]/choice[4]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "\"Y-yeah? And what about it?\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:294
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_SUSPICIOUS_SMUGGLER\"]/choice[4]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "You got anything to trade?"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:296
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_SUSPICIOUS_SMUGGLER\"]/choice[4]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "\"O-oh. Yeah, of course. Come aboard!\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:301
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_SUSPICIOUS_SMUGGLER\"]/choice[4]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Attack them!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:303
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_SUSPICIOUS_SMUGGLER\"]/choice[4]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "You prepare for combat."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:306
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_SUSPICIOUS_SMUGGLER\"]/choice[4]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:345
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The distress beacon is coming from a large Elite Harmony ship, but it's already starting to blow up! Scans don't seem to reveal any life signs inside, so it's not like you could have saved anyone.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tThere might be just enough time to catch the black box if you have a quick solution."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:351
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS\"]/choice[@req=\"temporal\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "A Temporal system could have helped here."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:355
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS\"]/choice[@req=\"temporal\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Temporal Manipulator) Slow down the black box's area and retrieve it."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:357
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS\"]/choice[@req=\"temporal\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your Temporal Manipulator allows you to retrieve the box comfortably. You "
"start scrapping the wreck during decoding."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:361
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS\"]/choice[@req=\"temporal\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:368
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_HIGH_SENSORS_AND_HACKING\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "With good Sensors and some Hacking we could have decoded it."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:372
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_HIGH_SENSORS_AND_HACKING\""
" and not(@lvl)]/text"
msgstr "(Sensors 2 + Hacking) Remotely decode it."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:374
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_HIGH_SENSORS_AND_HACKING\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It takes but a moment for your hacking drone to reach the black box and find"
" out what happened. You also start scrapping the wreck."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:378
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_HIGH_SENSORS_AND_HACKING\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:385
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_ENGI_AND_LANIUS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your Engi locates the box and says your Lanius could catch it before it's "
"too late."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:387
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_ENGI_AND_LANIUS\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Suggestion: throw metalvore through airlock in less than 8.7534 seconds. Chance of success = significant.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\tYou're not too sure about this, until your Lanius happily jumps out to grab the box like a kid chasing a tasty snack!\n"
"\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\tFortunately it's used to this type of acrobatics, and avoids any injuries while also bringing back some scrap.\n"
"\t\t\t\tIt adds, \"Ship tasted weird. Bit familiar.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:396
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_ENGI_AND_LANIUS\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:403
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS\"]/choice[6]/text"
msgstr "There's nothing we can do, just scrap whatever's left."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:405
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS\"]/choice[6]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You wait for the ship to finish blowing up, then enjoy the free scrap."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:409
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS\"]/choice[6]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:417
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_2\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"According to the box, the crew were crushed or impaled, and the ship sabotaged, save for the Life Support and Medbay.\n"
"\t\tA single shuttle managed to escape before the ship blew up. Another ship was present, maybe the ones who did this. You realize it's still here, docked not far from this beacon!\n"
"\n"
"\t\tClose enough to see what's up before jumping away."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:424
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_2\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "To that ship!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:426
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_2\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "You easily catch up to them, and they haven't noticed you yet."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:430
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_2\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"mind\"]/text"
msgstr "(Mind Control) Find out what happened."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:432
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_2\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"mind\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"We were selling mind torture devices to Engi Defenders. The deal went sour went something in their ship went on a rampage. A shuttle escaped. We ran.\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tThat solves the mystery. You also extract the shuttle's destination and leave like nothing happened."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:440
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_2\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"mind\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:447
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_2\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Hail them."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:449
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_2\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"The Feds are here for revenge! I told you we should have jumped away, Lisa.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\"But why? We're innocent! Why else would we still be here, just tell them that you numbnut!\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\"Hah! Like they would believe us, why are you always so naive? Charge the jump drive already!\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tIf you really think they could be innocent, you'll have to rough up their hull without killing them to get answers."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:460
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_2\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:467
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_2\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Forget it, let's leave."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:474
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_2\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "No thanks, finish scrapping then we're leaving."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:476
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_2\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Why take risks when there's scrap right here and more important things to "
"do?"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:480
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_2\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:490
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_DEFROMORIUS_SUSPICIOUS\"]/gotaway/text"
msgstr ""
"As the ship escapes, you ask around the dock but nobody tells you anything.\n"
"\t\t\tThere goes your only lead in this mystery. Back to the mission."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:494
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_DEFROMORIUS_SUSPICIOUS\"]/gotaway/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:499
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_DEFROMORIUS_SUSPICIOUS\"]/surrender/text"
msgstr ""
"\"It wasn't us! I beg you in the name of Lisa, stop! We'll tell you everything!\"\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\"Wait, what does that have to do with me? They don't even kno-... Oh, whatever.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:505
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_DEFROMORIUS_SUSPICIOUS\"]/surrender/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Ok, then who did this?"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:507
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_DEFROMORIUS_SUSPICIOUS\"]/surrender/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"We were just minding our own business, on the way to this dock to sell our trinkets...\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tAs you dig into their eyes with your hand ready to gesture \"Fire at will\", they adjust their story.\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\"Ok mayyyybe we were selling a little neural shocker or two to those Engis off the books. But then they started acting strange and sent a Distress signal. Being just humble merchants, we took it as a clue to get the hell away! Right, Lisa?\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\"Just tell him about the shuttle, numbnut! No crazy stuff, just the facts.\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\"Oh yeah, right! We detected this small vessel escaping, and scans said there was this big monster inside! Some kind of Frankenstein! You know what, that must be the killer right there, it was an inside job I tell you!\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tThey start rambling about various conspiracy theories while \"Lisa\" in the back looks increasingly worried about their mental health."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:520
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_DEFROMORIUS_SUSPICIOUS\"]/surrender/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "We believe you. Where did the shuttle go?"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:522
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_DEFROMORIUS_SUSPICIOUS\"]/surrender/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"As a security measure they had trackers in their merchandise. That gives you"
" the shuttle's destination."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:528
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_DEFROMORIUS_SUSPICIOUS\"]/surrender/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:537
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_DEFROMORIUS_SUSPICIOUS\"]/surrender/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "That's probably a lie, keep fighting!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:542
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_DEFROMORIUS_SUSPICIOUS\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The ship breaks apart and you salvage what you can. Maybe justice was "
"served, you can't really be sure."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:545
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_DEFROMORIUS_SUSPICIOUS\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Even if it wasn't them, scrap is scrap."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:550
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_DEFROMORIUS_SUSPICIOUS\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"With the crew dead you salvage what you can. Maybe justice was served, you "
"can't really be sure."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:553
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_DEFROMORIUS_SUSPICIOUS\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Even if it wasn't them, scrap is scrap."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:576
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_SHUTTLE\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr ""
"The destination of the creature likely responsible for goring the Engis."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:579
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_SHUTTLE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You quickly find the shuttle, which didn't get very far since it turns out it took serious damage at some point.\n"
"\t\tScans indeed reveal life inside, slowly fading. You detect markers of Engi Defender... and Lanius?... and something else too??\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tThat doesn't make sense since there's only 1 creature detected."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:586
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_SHUTTLE\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attempt to communicate with it."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:588
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_SHUTTLE\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"To your surprise, it does seem to be some sort of Engi Defender, and it definitely answers you like one.\n"
"\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\"Self = in jeopardy but know you = Federation. --COMPUTING-- This beacon = not likely your mission. Your presence here: purpose?\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:594
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_SHUTTLE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Did you kill the Engi Defenders?"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:596
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_SHUTTLE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Affirmative. Number of reasons to lie = 0. Self = anomaly. --PAIN-- \n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tAccidental discovery: Lanius metalflesh: can bind to Engi nanites. Requirements: matter from Shell forbidden experiments + extremely unlikely radiation burst. --STATISTICALLY IMPOSSIBLE-- Harmony verdict: undo or eliminate.\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tYou don't seem very convinced, but the creature keeps going.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\"Solution for survival: join the RadiKals. --OBJECTIVE COMPLETE-- However, Harmony = persistent. Captured me. Attempted to reset with: neural torture. Solution for escape: kill. --OBJECTIVE COMPLETE-- Now: your intents?\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:605
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_SHUTTLE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "We could protect you from the Harmony."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:607
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_SHUTTLE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Answer = unexpected. You = fools: 97% probability. Regardless, I cease functioning in: [time.short]\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe creature does look desperate for oxygen by now. You can't risk bringing it in just yet, but maybe you can help it remotely and see what happens."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:613
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_SHUTTLE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_OXYGENIZER\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "You don't have ways to sufficiently oxygenize outside of your ship."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:618
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_SHUTTLE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_OXYGENIZER\""
" and not(@lvl)]/text"
msgstr "(Oxygenizer) Help it breathe"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:623
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_SHUTTLE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"NANO_MEDBAY\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "You can't spread Medbay healing around."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:628
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_SHUTTLE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"NANO_MEDBAY\""
" and not(@lvl)]/text"
msgstr "(Med-bot Dispersal) Send it some help"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:633
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_SHUTTLE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_BOMBS_HEAL\"]/text"
msgstr "(Healing Bomb) Revive it"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:646
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_SHUTTLE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[6]/text"
msgstr "Leave it to die, it did deserve it."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:648
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_SHUTTLE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[6]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You wait for the creature to suffocate, thrashing around the ship as it does"
" so, then scrap the remains of the shuttle."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:653
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_SHUTTLE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[6]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:662
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_SHUTTLE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "We will avenge our allies."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:664
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_SHUTTLE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Outcome: expected. Solutions = none. Proceed, this = better than: lethal suffocation.\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tYou safely put the creature out of its misery from a distance, then scrap the remains of the shuttle."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:671
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_SHUTTLE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:682
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_SHUTTLE\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "This cannot end well, better leave now."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:688
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_OFFER\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Wow. This solution: ingenious. You = promising, now 51% probability. --NEW OBJECTIVE: JOIN YOU--\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\tLooks like you have new loyal crew. You ask their name.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\"Self ID = 'RK (Engi) Defender x Rockman-shaped-Morph x Lanius [amalgam]'.\n"
"\t\tElse If: you = limited brainpower, use alias 'Def_Rock-Morph_Lanius'.\"\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tYou decide 'Defromorius' will do. Once healed, it helps you fully scrap the shuttle and you're all ready to go."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:702
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_DEFROMORIUS_OFFER\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:729
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr ""
"You were told you can get great RadiKal Bam gear at this beacon, if you can "
"prove you're a customer."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:732
msgid "data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The planet here is surrounded by majestic, profitable, and highly hazardous asteroid rings, but you're far enough not to risk collisions.\n"
"\t\tThe longer and farther away you scan, the more auto-ships you detect harvesting minerals from them.\n"
"\t\tPlenty of manned ships are also practicing flight maneuvers, fighting each other in what seems to be friendly sparring, or patrolling. Some of those seem to have noticed you but haven't reacted so far.\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\tNow a hail is coming from the planet, which you take. \"Enjoying the view, Captain? Instead of just sitting there, show us you're a customer or get lost.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:741
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_BAM_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "You do not have any RK Bam gear."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:746
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_BAM_GEAR\""
" and not(@lvl)]/text"
msgstr "(RK Bam gear) Hit Hard..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:748
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_BAM_GEAR\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"... Homie! That's what I'm talking about. Here's the welcome gift. Hurry "
"up and come over so we can trade!\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:752
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_BAM_GEAR\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:759
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "You do not have any RK gear at all."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:764
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and not(@lvl)]/text"
msgstr "(any piece of RK gear) Business"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:766
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Nice. Hope you're bringing anything for us. We have gear. Hurry up and "
"come over so we can trade!\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:769
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:776
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_ANY_SACRIFICEABLE_MANTIS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Non-Unique Mantis) We have 'workpieces' for sale, could you direct us to "
"the right place?"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:778
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_ANY_SACRIFICEABLE_MANTIS\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Righto, then it's the Punk lab you want. I can send you there instead.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:783
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_ANY_SACRIFICEABLE_MANTIS\"]/event/choice[@req=\"rks_lab_coords_punk\"]/text"
msgstr "Alright then."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:785
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_ANY_SACRIFICEABLE_MANTIS\"]/event/choice[@req=\"rks_lab_coords_punk\"]/event/text"
msgstr "\"Tell them they stink while you're at it. Hah! Those smug freaks.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:794
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_ANY_SACRIFICEABLE_MANTIS\"]/event/choice[@req=\"rks_lab_coords_punk\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:798
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_ANY_SACRIFICEABLE_MANTIS\"]/event/choice[@req=\"rks_lab_coords_punk\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:805
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_ANY_SACRIFICEABLE_MANTIS\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "We already have that lab's coords, but thanks."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:813
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_ANY_SACRIFICEABLE_ORCHID\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Non-Unique Orchids) We have 'flammable material' for sale, could you direct"
" us to the right place?"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:815
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_ANY_SACRIFICEABLE_ORCHID\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Righto, then it's the Scorch lab you want. I can send you there instead.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:820
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_ANY_SACRIFICEABLE_ORCHID\"]/event/choice[@req=\"rks_lab_coords_scorch\"]/text"
msgstr "Alright then."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:822
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_ANY_SACRIFICEABLE_ORCHID\"]/event/choice[@req=\"rks_lab_coords_scorch\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Tell them they stink while you're at it. Hah! That's gonna make their "
"blood boil.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:831
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_ANY_SACRIFICEABLE_ORCHID\"]/event/choice[@req=\"rks_lab_coords_scorch\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:835
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_ANY_SACRIFICEABLE_ORCHID\"]/event/choice[@req=\"rks_lab_coords_scorch\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:842
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_ANY_SACRIFICEABLE_ORCHID\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "We already have that lab's coords, but thanks."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:850
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[7]/text"
msgstr "Is this the Giant Carousel?"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:852
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[7]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your ship soon takes damage from a source you cannot identify. \"F**k off, "
"tourist. You had been warned.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:856
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[7]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:860
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[7]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:867
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[8]/text"
msgstr "We're just passing through here, don't mind us."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:869
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[8]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"There is no answer. You move a safe distance away and figure you have time to do some maintenance.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\tAfter some time, you detect some Shell ships jumping in weapons hot, but you're safe here."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:874
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[8]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:878
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM\"]/choice[8]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:886
msgid "data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM_2\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"So, what've you got? Anything hard, or explosive? And breathing? Or even inanimate, that's fine too, we're not like the Scorch.\" He says that like they're so much better, but you don't think it's a good idea to point that out.\n"
"\n"
"\t\tYou look at what they want and get a better understanding of why this sector is outlawed by so many factions. However the mission comes first, right?"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:893
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM_2\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_ANY_SACRIFICEABLE_SHELL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You don't have Shells for this (Uniques would rather kill you and "
"themselves)"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:898
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM_2\"]/choice[@req=\"shell\"]/text"
msgstr "A Shell."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:900
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM_2\"]/choice[@req=\"shell\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Explodey ball, always nice. Here's your cash.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\tYou can feel the rest of your crew judging you."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:910
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM_2\"]/choice[@req=\"shell\"]/event/removeCrew/text"
msgstr "You cannot clone crew that you sold away to a painful death."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:914
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM_2\"]/choice[@req=\"shell\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Moving on..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:945
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM_2\"]/choice[@req=\"shell_guardian\"]/text"
msgstr "A Guardian."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:947
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_BAM_2\"]/choice[@req=\"shell_guardian\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Explodey-er ball! Here's big cash!\"\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\tYou can feel the rest of your crew judging you."

