#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1067
msgid "data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_LAB_BAM_AMBUSH\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You barely even reach the Jump button as a small Shell fleet jumps in! A very angry Radiant ship immediately hails you.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\"Federation simpletons, don't get me wrong, these guys actually do cool science, and we even know a few of our rogue elites are high-ranking in there.\"\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tFor a brief moment, you think this is gonna end peacefully.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\t\"But it's at our expense, plus they make a lot of breaches, like, A LOT! It's crazy. Anyway our management just can't tolerate all this anymore and unfortunately letting you just fly out of there alive would look bad for us.\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\tYou wonder why they would expose themselves to weaponry so specifically good against their biology, but your scans reveal they came quite prepared!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1081
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_LAB_BAM_AMBUSH\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_alkali\"]/text"
msgstr "(Alkali) Speaking of, make way idiots. Secret mission."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1086
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_LAB_BAM_AMBUSH\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "...Guess that's the price of business."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1088
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_LAB_BAM_AMBUSH\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Ah shit, here we go again. The Geniocracy is back, pals. You know what to do: EXPLOSIONS!\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\tProjectiles from the RK Bam and the assault fleet start flying in every direction!\n"
"\t\t\t\tAlso, they must have used a special jammer to depower your jump drive, you will have to charge it again."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1097
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_LAB_BAM_AMBUSH\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1106
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_LAB_BAM_ATTACKER\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The Elite Shell ship breaks apart and you quickly salvage what you can "
"before the rest of the fleet realizes what happened."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1109
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_LAB_BAM_ATTACKER\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "The Shells are messed up, but we might be worse."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1114
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_LAB_BAM_ATTACKER\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"With the crew dead you quickly salvage what you can from the Elite Shell "
"ship before the rest of the fleet realizes what happened."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1117
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_LAB_BAM_ATTACKER\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "The Shells are messed up, but we might be worse."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1145
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_PUNK\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr ""
"You were told you can get great RadiKal Punk gear at this beacon, if you can"
" prove you're a customer."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1148
msgid "data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_PUNK\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"So much blue. Not an island in sight, this planet is covered in water. And when you look closely, a few floating structures. A few hovering ones too.\n"
"\t\tDeeper scans can only penetrate the endless ocean so much, but reveal vast underwater facilities dedicated to the study of who-knows-what. Probably hidden for good reason.\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\tYou take an incoming hail. \"Ho hooo, a visitor. A quiet one at that. Maybe here for quiet affairs? Then show proof.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1156
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_PUNK\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_PUNK_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "You do not have any RK Punk gear."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1161
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_PUNK\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_PUNK_GEAR\""
" and not(@lvl)]/text"
msgstr "(RK Punk gear) Stay Smart..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1163
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_PUNK\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_PUNK_GEAR\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"... Slayer. Heheh. A drone will bring you the welcome gift. We await "
"you.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1167
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_PUNK\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_PUNK_GEAR\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1174
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_PUNK\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "You do not have any RK gear at all."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1179
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_PUNK\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and not(@lvl)]/text"
msgstr "(any piece of RK gear) Business"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1181
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_PUNK\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Yes yes... Let's do business. We are in need of a few things. We await "
