"\"I take great pleasure in watching new workpieces arrive. Are you going to please me? HAH I'm just teasing you. But really, anything?\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\tYou look at the list of \"workpieces\" in-demand and what you just heard only gets more creepy."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1234
