msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_PUNK_3\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Enough pleasantries, welcome to our best local store. I'm hearing voices... HAH gotcha, no, not like that. In my earpiece, sounds urgent. Be seeing you.\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\tBefore you shop, you still have some time to do something else aboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1372
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_PUNK_3\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1376
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_PUNK_3\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1382
msgid "data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_LAB_PUNK_AMBUSH\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You barely even reach the Jump button as a small Free Mantis fleet jumps in! A very Warlord ship immediately hails you.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\"Federation, federation. You our heroes! So WHY you here, doing evil trade??!\" The already drugged-up Warlord looks devastated but is back on the warpath before you can even answer. \"We come to kill them, but you with them! We kill you too!\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\tYou wonder why they would come to people so adept at killing their kind (and everybody else too), but your scans reveal they came quite prepared!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1392
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_LAB_PUNK_AMBUSH\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_MANTIS_UNIQUE\"]/text"
msgstr "(Unique Mantis) TskKAK! Let pass! Secret mission."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1397
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_LAB_PUNK_AMBUSH\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "...Makes sense, really."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1399
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_LAB_PUNK_AMBUSH\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"So much vigor, so little intellect, and we have so. many. guns. Butler drone, tell the staff to get off their arses. And prepare my tea.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\tProjectiles from the RK Punk and the assault fleet start flying in every direction!\n"
"\t\t\t\tAlso, they must have used a special jammer to depower your jump drive, you will have to charge it again."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1408
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_LAB_PUNK_AMBUSH\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1416
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_LAB_PUNK_ATTACKER\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The Elite Free Mantis ship breaks apart and you quickly salvage what you can"
" before the rest of the fleet realizes what happened."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1419
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_LAB_PUNK_ATTACKER\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Let's hope they remain such hardcore fans after this."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1424
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_LAB_PUNK_ATTACKER\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"With the crew dead you quickly salvage what you can from the Elite Free "
"Mantis ship before the rest of the fleet realizes what happened."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1427
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_LAB_PUNK_ATTACKER\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Let's hope they remain such hardcore fans after this."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1453
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr ""
"You were told you can get great RadiKal Scorch gear at this beacon, if you "
"can prove you're a customer."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1456
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You arrive at a red planet with volcanoes so large you can see them from orbit, and around them, a multitude of structures that look like giant insects. The atmosphere looks like it's on fire.\n"
"\t\tTaking a closer look, you notice that many of the \"structures\" actually move, sampling lava, putting things in it, and doing all sorts of strange experiments.\n"
"\t\tYou can also tell that there are many scientific facilities, factories and even what looks like stadiums all over the surface, a good distance away from the lava flows.\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\tSomeone on the planet is hailing you. \"We see you, Federation Renegade. If you have reason to be here, now's time to show proof.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1465
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_SCORCH_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "You do not have any RK Scorch gear."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1470
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_SCORCH_GEAR\""
" and not(@lvl)]/text"
msgstr "(RK Scorch gear) Burn Bright..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1472
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_SCORCH_GEAR\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"... Brother. It always warms the heart to see one of us. Here is the "
"welcome gift. You are cleared to land.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1476
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_SCORCH_GEAR\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1483
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "You do not have any RK gear at all."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1488
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and not(@lvl)]/text"
msgstr "(any piece of RK gear) Business"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1490
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Good. We've been awaiting some deliveries, and have quite the stockpile of"
" equipment to sell. Let's trade then. You are cleared to land.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1493
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1500
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH\"]/choice[5]/text"
msgstr "Is this the Bakery Planet?"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1502
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH\"]/choice[5]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your ship soon takes damage from a source you cannot identify. \"Begone, "
"tourist. You had been warned.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1506
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH\"]/choice[5]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1510
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH\"]/choice[5]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1517
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH\"]/choice[6]/text"
msgstr "We're just passing through here, don't mind us."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1519
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH\"]/choice[6]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"There is no answer. You move a safe distance away and figure you have time to do some maintenance.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\tAfter some time, you detect some Orchid ships jumping in weapons hot, but you're safe here."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1524
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH\"]/choice[6]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1528
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH\"]/choice[6]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1536
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH_2\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"First, the deliveries. What raw materials do you bring? The furnaces, vivisection labs and distilleries hunger.\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\tYou look at the list of \"materials\" and get a better understanding of why this sector is outlawed by so many factions. However the mission comes first, right?"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1543
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH_2\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_ANY_SACRIFICEABLE_ORCHID\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You don't have Orchids for this (Uniques would rather kill you and "
"themselves)"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1548
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH_2\"]/choice[@req=\"orchid\"]/text"
msgstr "An Orchid."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1550
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH_2\"]/choice[@req=\"orchid\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"The base material. Always useful. Here's your payment.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\tYou can feel the rest of your crew judging you."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1560
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH_2\"]/choice[@req=\"orchid\"]/event/removeCrew/text"
msgstr "You cannot clone crew that you sold away to a painful death."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1564
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH_2\"]/choice[@req=\"orchid\"]/event/choice/text"
