"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH_2\"]/choice[@req=\"orchid_praetor\"]/event/removeCrew/text"
msgstr "You cannot clone crew that you sold away to a painful death."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1633
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH_2\"]/choice[@req=\"orchid_praetor\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Moving on..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1639
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH_2\"]/choice[@req=\"orchid_cultivator\"]/text"
msgstr "A Cultivator."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1641
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH_2\"]/choice[@req=\"orchid_cultivator\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Quality material, yes. Here's greater payment.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\tYou can feel the rest of your crew judging you."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1652
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH_2\"]/choice[@req=\"orchid_cultivator\"]/event/removeCrew/text"
msgstr "You cannot clone crew that you sold away to a painful death."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1656
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH_2\"]/choice[@req=\"orchid_cultivator\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Moving on..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1663
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH_2\"]/choice[@req=\"ORCHID_KIDS\"]/text"
msgstr "Orchid children."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1665
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH_2\"]/choice[@req=\"ORCHID_KIDS\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Fantastic! These are increasingly difficult to come by, as if the Orchids are tightening security over time. Here's your generous payment.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\tYou can feel the rest of your crew looking at you in disgust, but nobody dares say anything."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1679
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH_2\"]/choice[@req=\"ORCHID_KIDS\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Moving on..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1686
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH_2\"]/choice[8]/text"
msgstr "Nothing, I'm afraid."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1691
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH_2\"]/choice[9]/text"
msgstr "Actually... we have an emergency, bye!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1697
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH_3\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Alright, now enjoy our best local store. I'm getting some pressing reports that I have to look into. Pleasure doing business and all.\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\tBefore you shop, you still have some time to do something else aboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1705
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH_3\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1709
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_QUEST_LAB_SCORCH_3\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1717
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_LAB_SCORCH_AMBUSH\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You barely even reach the Jump button as a small Orchid fleet jumps in! A very angry Praetor ship immediately hails you.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\"Federation. Scouts saw you engage with these people. You traitorous pest. We will avenge our people. Then raze this abomination of a planet.\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\tYou wonder why they would expose themselves to weaponry so specifically good against their biology, but your scans reveal they came quite prepared!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1727
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_LAB_SCORCH_AMBUSH\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_HAS_ORCHID_UNIQUE\"]/text"
msgstr "(Unique Orchid) Let us go. Secret mission."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1732
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_LAB_SCORCH_AMBUSH\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "...To be honest, I expected something like this."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1734
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_LAB_SCORCH_AMBUSH\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Goddamn Florals, why must you always try and stop progress? It's not our fault if these bodies make the best fuel! We didn't make the rules. Guards, it's time to do some gardening!\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\tProjectiles from the RK Scorch and the assault fleet start flying in every direction!\n"
"\t\t\t\tAlso, they must have used a special jammer to depower your jump drive, you will have to charge it again."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1743
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_LAB_SCORCH_AMBUSH\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1752
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_LAB_SCORCH_ATTACKER\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The Elite Orchid ship breaks apart and you quickly salvage what you can "
"before the rest of the fleet realizes what happened."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1755
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_LAB_SCORCH_ATTACKER\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Now we're killing Elite allies to defend arms dealers. Okay."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1760
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_LAB_SCORCH_ATTACKER\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"With the crew dead you quickly salvage what you can from the Elite Orchid "
"ship before the rest of the fleet realizes what happened."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1763
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RKS_LAB_SCORCH_ATTACKER\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Now we're killing Elite allies to defend arms dealers. Okay."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1795
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_PIRATE_TRINITY\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr ""
"The pirates await your scrap. Disappoint them in any way at your own risk!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1798
msgid "data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_PIRATE_TRINITY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The pirate clans don't always see eye to eye, but when there's big money to be made, they know how to behave. The elite welcoming you here seems in charge of overseeing the transactions.\n"
"\t\t\"Sssso, you're the big shot Feddy cusssstomer who threw away a lawful life to mingle with ussss, eh? No offensssse but I've gotta tell you, I don't really buy it. We shall ssssee if you're for real...\"\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tIf you don't want to anger the slug and his ruthless associates, you had better buy something from each of the pirate subfactions.\n"
"\t\tIt's all-or-nothing, but if you do, pirates everywhere will respect you that much more!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1810
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_PIRATE_TRINITY\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Yep that's me. Enough chitchat, show us the goods."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1818
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_PIRATE_TRINITY\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Not us, just passing through."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1835
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_PIRATE_TRINITY_CHOOSE\"]/text"
msgstr "The pirates are all looking at you expectantly."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1841
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_PIRATE_TRINITY_CHOOSE\"]/choice[@req=\"rks_pirate_trinity_met_slaver\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "Meet with the Tiiikaka slaver"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1851
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_PIRATE_TRINITY_CHOOSE\"]/choice[@req=\"rks_pirate_trinity_met_slaver\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "The slaver is counting their scrap, seated on a slave's face."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1856
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_PIRATE_TRINITY_CHOOSE\"]/choice[@req=\"rks_pirate_trinity_met_mercenary\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "Meet with the Syndicate mercenary"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1860
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_PIRATE_TRINITY_CHOOSE\"]/choice[@req=\"rks_pirate_trinity_met_mercenary\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "The mercenary is juggling bits of scrap, knives and loaded guns."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1865
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_PIRATE_TRINITY_CHOOSE\"]/choice[@req=\"rks_pirate_trinity_met_smuggler\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "Meet with the Argeonn smuggler"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1869
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_PIRATE_TRINITY_CHOOSE\"]/choice[@req=\"rks_pirate_trinity_met_smuggler\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "The smuggler is telling their third wife she can buy that Butler."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1875
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_PIRATE_TRINITY_CHOOSE\"]/choice[@req=\"rks_pirate_trinity_count\"]/text"
msgstr "Thank them for the business and say goodbye."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1877
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_PIRATE_TRINITY_CHOOSE\"]/choice[@req=\"rks_pirate_trinity_count\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Well well, you truly are one rich, ssssick individual with zero regard for other living thingsss, a fantasssstic customer by all accountssss! Accept my apologiesss for doubting you, and may your raidsss bring great bounty! Galsss and guyssss, IT'SSS PARTY TIME! Narcoticsss for everyone, and a round of Shoot-Tha-Limbs on that human sssslave who looked at me funny thisss morning!\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\tThey let you leave with a little gift and big smiles on their faces. Congratulations, you have just made the galaxy a worse place."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1884
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_PIRATE_TRINITY_CHOOSE\"]/choice[@req=\"rks_pirate_trinity_count\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1892
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_PIRATE_TRINITY_CHOOSE\"]/choice[8]/text"
msgstr "We won't actually do business with all of you. We're leaving."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1898
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_PIRATE_TRINITY_CHOOSE_SLAVER\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"From warships, mining camps, nurseries, outposts too, we bring best and brightest slaves! Sure one of them is your need...\n"
"\t\tUnless you no wanna pay. Then we put slave collar on you too.\""

