"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_PIRATE_TRINITY_CHOOSE_SLAVER\"]/choice/event/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "You know what, the funny thing is, we're broke..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1965
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_PIRATE_TRINITY_CHOOSE_SLAVER\"]/choice/event/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Bad words feddy captain, should have choose better words. But mostly should have bring scrap.\" The pirate ship in front of you instantly makes itself combat ready, having clearly expected that. \n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tYou can't tell whether the slug overseer is furious, vindicated, or both. \"Hah! I knew it, you just wanted to take down a bunch of piratesss at once you wannabe hero. Guesss what, we're not that dumb! Hey Kurt, hand over the scrap, i won the bet.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tWith that, they and the other pirate ships jump away, leaving you to deal with the slaver!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1972
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_PIRATE_TRINITY_CHOOSE_SLAVER\"]/choice/event/choice[4]/event/choice/text"
