msgstr ""
"\"Stay one step ahead of your enemies with our intelligence services. From recon to distraction, all the way to more ...decisive action once we're acquainted well enough!\n"
"\t\tAssuming you didn't make yourself our next target by coming here empty-handed, obviously.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1988
