msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_PIRATE_TRINITY_CHOOSE_MERCENARY\"]/choice/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Bad choice, captain. You should have brought that scrap.\" The pirate ship in front of you instantly makes itself combat ready, having clearly expected that. \n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tYou can't tell whether the slug overseer is furious, vindicated, or both. \"Hah! I knew it, you just wanted to take down a bunch of piratesss at once you wannabe hero. Guesss what, we're not that dumb! Hey Kurt, hand over the scrap, i won the bet.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tWith that, they and the other pirate ships jump away, leaving you to deal with the mercenary!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:2037
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_PIRATE_TRINITY_CHOOSE_MERCENARY\"]/choice/event/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:2047
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_PIRATE_TRINITY_CHOOSE_SMUGGLER\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Do you know what separates good captains from great captains? Well, we do, and that's where they procure their weaponry. We provide those extra special weapons and augments that go beyond what you can find in your everyday store.\n"
"\t\tAnd where did we get them? In the lifeless ships of non-paying captains, which you're too smart to be, right?\""

